  "body": "![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/33201827/66103528-b475f400-e5d3-11e9-9669-611d566eed19.png)\r\n\r\nSome users have reported being penalised despite having their validator consistently attesting to the current head. The above image contains the logs of a validator which has been penalised.\r\n\r\n1) Attestations are not being included properly, which leads to momentary penalties.\r\n20 Messages not being successfully propagated through gossipsub, which leads to the attestation going missing\r\n\r\nThis issue is to track this bug\r\n\r\nPossibly Related to #3691 ",
